OL,3,CMenu calorie labelling fails to
OL,4,Cencourage healthier options
OL,6,FCalorie labelling in restaurants and
OL,7,Fcafes has not resulted in customers
OL,8,Fchoosing healthier meals, a study
OL,9,Fsuggests.
OL,11,FMandatory calorie labelling was
OL,12,Fintroduced in England for businesses
OL,13,Fthat serve food in April 2022 as part
OL,14,Fof the government's national obesity
OL,15,Fstrategy, with the aim of helping
OL,16,Fdiners make healthier choices.
