OL,3,CMenu calorie labelling fails to
OL,4,Cencourage healthier options
OL,6,FMore than 6,500 customers provided
OL,7,Finformation about their calorie
OL,8,Fconsumption, their awareness and use
OL,9,Fof calorie information and their
OL,10,Funderstanding of the amount of
OL,11,Fcalories in their meals.
OL,13,FThe study, published in Nature Human
OL,14,FBehaviour, found "no meaningful
OL,15,Fdecrease" in the number of calories
OL,16,Fbought or consumed after mandatory
OL,17,Flabelling was introduced.
