OL,3,CMenu calorie labelling fails to
OL,4,Cencourage healthier options
OL,6,FLead researcher Dr Megan Polden said:
OL,7,F"The introduction of mandatory calorie
OL,8,Flabelling alone was not associated
OL,9,Fwith significant dietary changes in
OL,10,Fout-of-home food settings."
OL,12,FProfessor Eric Robinson said:
OL,13,F"However, we know that many businesses
OL,14,Fhave not been providing calorie
OL,15,Flabelling as recommended and some
OL,16,Fbusinesses have not provided any
OL,17,Fcalorie labelling at all, which of
OL,18,Fcourse may explain our results.
