OL,6,F"Our results may also indicate that a
OL,7,Fcombination of strategies, such as
OL,8,Fimproved business compliance measure,
OL,9,Fpublic education on calorie intake and
OL,10,Fclearer labelling, could be necessary
OL,11,Fto support healthier consumer choices."
